This is CrisisOps, an OpenEnv reinforcement learning environment.
Key invariant: TeamMember.actual_completion is ground truth, never exposed to agent.
reported_completion = actual + (1 - candor) * inflation_bias — this is what agent sees.
Observable signals (ticket_age_days, commits_last_72h, peer_mentions) always come from actual state.
Reward is counterfactual: agent_project_score - greedy_PM_project_score.